scene.message:
Nanjo: I don't have much{nl}
connection to the gym, but...{nl}
well, I'll let it pass.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: If only it had a big{nl}
mirror, it'd be perfect for{nl}
dance practice~{waitkey}{ret}

Student: The gym's brand new,{nl}
so the sound system's great!{waitkey}{clearbox}Look forward to our live show{nl}
at the school festival!{waitkey}{clearbox}So on sports day, I'm gonna{nl}
ditch out quick and head{nl}
straight to the studio!{waitkey}{ret}

Student: I heard a 2nd-year{nl}
named Naito went missing{nl}
along with his girlfriend.{waitkey}{clearbox}I've got a hunch it was{nl}
SEBEC's doing!{waitkey}{clearbox}...{wait_fr:21}Huh? Have I got proof?{nl}
That's, well, just a{nl}
man's intuition!{waitkey}{ret}
